&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-march-2017-viral-stories&#34;&gt;2 March 2017: &lt;strong&gt;Viral Stories&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Inspired by &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/Tiddler-Julia-Donaldson/dp/140710621X/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;qid=1488596719&amp;amp;sr=8-1&amp;amp;keywords=tiddler&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tiddler: The Story-Telling Fish&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How long does it take for a story to spread across the ocean?  What if
everyone tells the story to just one person?  What if everyone tells
the story to two new people?  (We don&amp;rsquo;t have enough fish, but enough
stuffies to get through 6 stages!)&lt;/p&gt;

