&lt;h3 id=&#34;23-february-2017-crazy-calendars&#34;&gt;23 February 2017: &lt;strong&gt;Crazy Calendars&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Calendars are puzzles - the last day of this month, first with the
first day of the next month.  There are different shapes of months
because the number of days is either 30 or 31, and February is really
odd.&lt;/p&gt;

